    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely in love with this car, but it's time for it to find a new home. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it since day one. The paint is sparkling, the interior is spotless, and it still has that wonderful 'new car' feel. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
