    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of the S54B32 high-revving straight-six. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing service, addressing the chassis and internal longevity concerns common to the platform. The double-VANOS system has been precision-timed and overhauled for optimal variable valve lift. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a tight limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true to factory kinematics with no bushing deflection. The exterior finish is flawless, free of swirl marks or orange peel, while the interior maintains its original tactile integrity. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key machine for the purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
