    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a deep, glass-like exterior finish completely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the factory alloy wheels are devoid of even the slightest curb rash. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, with zero bolster wear or creasing. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive climate control, function with factory-standard precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
